-- Russia to Pick Coal Projects for $6 Billion China Energy Loan by Year-End
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2010-10-25T07:18:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/russia-to-pick-coal-projects-for-6-billion-china-energy-loan-by-year-end.html
Russia and China will select coal
projects by the end of this year that will use some of $6
billion of loans the Asian country has offered in return for
fuel supplies, Deputy Energy Minister Anatoly Yanovsky told
reporters today in Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
